></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mlt1665702695130.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mlt1665702695130.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mlt1665702695130.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mlt1665702695130\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $msgsrc\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mlt1665702695130___msgsrc_275273\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the component instance that sent the message.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__topic_d86171e1_d86172e1_d86173e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__p_d86174e1_d86175e1_d86176e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$msgsrc</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__section_w373ab1b7b5_w374ab1b7_w375ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__p_d86177e1_d86178e1_d86179e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">putmess \"Message received from %%$msgsrc.\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__topic_d57307e1_d57308e1_d57309e1_d57310e1_d57311e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022470e75\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__p_d86183e1_d86184e1_d86185e1\">String identifying the component instance that sent the message, if the receiveMessage trigger was activated by a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">postmessage</span> statement. The string contains all the path information necessary to reply to the message.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__p_d86186e1_d86187e1_d86188e1\">In addition, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$msgid</span> returns a non-empty string. If the receiveMessage trigger was not activated by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">postmessage</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$msgid</span> returns an empty string (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__topic_d57312e1_d57313e1_d57314e1_d57315e1_d57316e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022470e102\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__p_d86192e1_d86193e1_d86194e1\">Allowed only in a receiveMessage trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__p_d86195e1_d86196e1_d86197e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__section_bjy_sff_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1022470e115\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$msgsrc</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following code could appear in the receiveMessage trigger of a\n               component:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__pre_yxl_tff_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">postmessage $msgsrc, \"MSG001\", \"Reply to sender: message received.\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">To handle messages that are incorrectly addressed, the following code\n               could appear in the receiveMessage trigger of the application.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mlt1665702695130__pre_zxl_tff_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">postmessage $msgsrc, \"MSG001\", \"Reply to sender: instance addressed is unknown\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wtd1665702577667.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>postmessage</a><p>Send a message from one component instance to another.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702577585.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$msgdata</a><p>Return the message data received from postmessage.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ait1719676813154.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$msgdst</a><p>Return the name of the component instance to which a message was addressed.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zhv1719424135134.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$msgid</a><p>Return the identifier for a message received from postmessage.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jdo1665702577507.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$msginfo</a><p>Return the requested information about the latest message.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger receiveMessage</a><p>Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529975\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529975\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$msgsrc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $msgsrc Return the name of the component instance that sent the message. $msgsrc Example: putmess \"Message received from %%$msgsrc.\" Return Values String identifying the component instance that sent the message, if the receiveMessage trigger was activated by a postmessage statement. The string contains all the path information necessary to reply to the message. In addition, $msgid returns a non-empty string. If the receiveMessage trigger was not activated by postmessage , $msgid returns an empty string ( \"\" ). Use Allowed only in a receiveMessage trigger. Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $msgsrc The following code could appear in the receiveMessage trigger of a component: postmessage $msgsrc, \"MSG001\", \"Reply to sender: message received.\" Copy To handle messages that are incorrectly addressed, the following code could appear in the receiveMessage trigger of the application. postmessage $msgsrc, \"MSG001\", \"Reply to sender: instance addressed is unknown\" Copy Related Links postmessage Send a message from one component instance to another. $msgdata Return the message data received from postmessage. $msgdst Return the name of the component instance to which a message was addressed. $msgid Return the identifier for a message received from postmessage. $msginfo Return the requested information about the latest message. trigger receiveMessage Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}